verbose_text: Our qPCR studies indicate that prior to wounding many ephrins and Eph receptors are expressed within murine skin; all ephrin-Bs and EphBs are expressed to varying degrees, as are all ephrin-As, but only EphA1, A2, A4, and A7 are expressed at above background levels (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A).
evidence: EphA1, A2, A4, and A7 are expressed
